"ASCII control characters can also be encoded in the same way, i.e., \\t for "
"tab, etc., but are not required to be so encoded."
msgstr ""
"This field has only one special requirement.  Newline characters (Unix "
"newline characters, ASCII line feed) ''must'' be encoded as \\n.  Other "
"ASCII control characters can also be encoded in the same way, i.e., \\t for "
"tab, etc., but are not required to be so encoded."

